-- ICBC's Plan to Invest in Cathay Venture in Shanghai May Fail, Daily Says
-- Weiyi Lim
-- 2010-07-15T00:25:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-15/icbc-s-plan-to-invest-in-cathay-venture-in-shanghai-may-fail-daily-says.html

          
          
             Industrial & Commercial Bank of
China Ltd.’s plan to invest in Cathay Life Insurance Co.’s
venture in Shanghai may fail because Cathay wants to retain a
controlling stake, the Economic Daily News reported, without
saying where it got the information.  
